Wifi Connection Via CMD of Pi :

nmcli device wifi list 
nmcli device wifi connect "ESP32-AP" password "12345678"

go>>wifi>>advance options >> Edit Connection, because sometimes 
it stucks !!!! NOT IT !!!!

also you can change the ESP32-AP mode to Hotspot from Client. 
go >> wifi >> advance options >> Edit Connection >> select "ESP32-AP" 
>> goto gear. > wireless >> Mode >> Hotspot !!!!! NOT IT !!!!!

